    </p>

    <h3>4. Security</h3>
    <p>
        We implement standard security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access or disclosure.
    </p>

    <h3>5. Your Rights</h3>
    <p>
        You can request deletion of uploaded data or contact the admin for any privacy concerns.
    </p>

